item.title: Keep calm and get more Dakka T-Shirt
item.description: ** DAKKA!! DAKKA!! DAKKA ** All across the universe from the lowliest Grot to da krumpinest Warboss, there is one secret truth known to all: keep calm and get more DAKKA!!! This t-shirt is everything you’ve dreamed of and more. It feels soft and lightweight, with the right amount of stretch. It’s comfortable and flattering for all. • 100% combed and ring-spun cotton (Heather colors contain polyester) • Fabric weight: 4.
